description: Aberdeen Parks and Recreation — Activity Center, parks, programs, and recreational services for all residents.
breadcrumb:
  - label: Boards
    url: /boards/
  - label: Parks & Recreation
---

<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">

    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Aberdeen Parks & Recreation oversees the City's parks, open spaces, recreation programs, and the Aberdeen Activity Center. The department works to provide quality recreational opportunities for residents of all ages and abilities.</p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Aberdeen Activity Center</h2>
      <div class="bg-gov-blue-light rounded-xl p-5">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-3">The Aberdeen Activity Center serves as the community hub for recreation programs, fitness, and events.</p>
        <dl class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
          <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Address</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">7 Franklin Street, Aberdeen, MD 21001</dd></div>
          <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Phone</dt><dd><a href="tel:+14102721600" class="text-gov-blue hover:underline">(410) 272-1600</a></dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Programs &amp; Services</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {% for item in ["Fitness & Recreation Programs", "Youth Sports Leagues", "Senior Programs", "Community Events & Festivals", "Park Maintenance & Improvements", "Field & Facility Reservations"] %}
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-gov-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          {{ item }}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Upcoming Events</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        {% for event in events.community %}
        <a href="{{ event.url }}" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-center leading-none">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-80 uppercase">{{ event.month }}</span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold">{{ event.day }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors duration-200">{{ event.title }}</div>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/calendar-by-event-type/1367%2B1368%2B1369" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">All community events →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <aside>
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-24 space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">Contact</h2>
      <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Phone</dt><dd><a href="tel:+14102721600" class="text-gov-blue hover:underline">(410) 272-1600</a></dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Activity Center</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">7 Franklin Street<br/>Aberdeen, MD 21001</dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">City Hall Hours</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Mon–Fri, 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM</dd></div>
      </dl>
      <div class="pt-2 space-y-2">
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/parks-and-recreation" class="block w-full text-center bg-gov-blue text-white text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200">Official Parks Page</a>
        <a href="{{ '/events/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:border-gov-blue hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">All Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
